\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 What is the law of property? Could it be said that it is the law relating to physical objects such as a house, land}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7241145 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  a car \'85 etc? Or is it a branch of law dealing with or governing relations between a person and things or objects?
