\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight7\insrsid2119398\charrsid6322372 Not every transaction, right, or liability relating to physical objects/ material things/ is regarded as relevant to the law of property, for instan
ce, a contract between an owner of a car and a garage to service the car is part of law of contract rather than the law of property.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  
