/ have an effect that is more specific to property rights and are governed by the law of property}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  than the law of torts. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\highlight7\insrsid2119398\charrsid13644873 However, nuisances committed by a person with no proprietary claim are more part of torts than property law}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 .
