\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 For instance, in a case between Amleset Teame and W/ro Almaz Wolde and Ato Berhane G/yesus, in Civil File No 158191,
 the plaintiff was a minor when her father died in 1993 and the share of money from her father\rquote s inheritance was deposited at the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5327653\charrsid11362428  Commercial Bank of Ethiopia T/H}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 aimanot branch in the name of the defendants but on her behalf. Now the plaintiff who has attai
ned the age of majority has instituted an action for declaration of her ownership to the money plus interests thereto. The first defendant admitted the claim of the plaintiff while the 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\super\insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 nd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  defendant was earlier expelled from the country and the case was seen in his absence.
