\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 As we have seen earlier, property is frequently defined as the rights of a person with respect to a thing. However, this definiti
on is of little importance in legal discourse because a thing cannot have meaning full legal relationship with a person, for example, a thing cannot bring or defend a lawsuit. Property law does not deal with the rights, privileges in the abstract; it deal
s with relationships between and among persons.
\par With this in mind, one may define }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid11429162 property law as the complex of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid11429162 
legal relationships between and among persons with respect to things.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 It is a branch of law which }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 deals with and regulates the property rights}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381  i.e. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 the real rights /rights in-rem/}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381  a person exercises over a certain object which include }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 rights to use}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 , to collect and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 enjoy the fruits of}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 to transfer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 
 (by sale, donation or inheritance) and even }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 abandon the object}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381  and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\highlight3\insrsid2119398\charrsid1199381 exclude others.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  
