\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 According to George Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel, }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\insrsid2119398\charrsid474462 a human person is merely an abstract unit of free will or autonomy that does not have a concrete existence until that will acts on the external wor}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
