\par The theories discussed above in connection with the origin of private property are also used }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15357741\charrsid11362428 to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 
