\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 The treatment of things as accessories of another thing shall have the following effects.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
