s
. Hence, if it is a claim of title to a specific thing/ res/, the action is in-rem, for example, a claim of ownership of land or a sheep. However, if the claim is framed as an obligation, for instance, a claim for performance of a contract of sale of land
 or a ship, such right is personal. There was no difference between movables and immovable.
