\insrsid15664118\charrsid11362428 \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 possession}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15664118\charrsid11362428 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 
