\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 1.\tab}}\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-360\li360\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar
\jclisttab\tx360\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls30\adjustright\rin0\lin360\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 
It aids the criminal law by preserving the peace and order as the latter  is best secured by protecting a possessor and leaving the true owner if there is one to seek his remedy in a court of law.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}It is protected as part of the law of the fort since it is an extension of the protection, which the law throws around persons. 

\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}}\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-360\li360\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar
