It is protected as part of law of property because it is difficult to know that the possession in question is unlawful. A
t times when proof of title is difficult and transfer of property require intricate formalities, it would have been unjust to cast on every man whose possession was disturbed the burden of proving a flawless title. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2119398 
