 relation to water resources is a use right provided by the Water Resources Management Proclamation N}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \ul\insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 
 197/2000. However, water shall be private property where it is collected in a man made reservoir, basin or cistern from which it does not flow naturally. See Art 1229 of the Civil Code.
