e is a presumption that the owner/holder of the land owns what is constructed on it. However, this presumption is refutable if the owner of a building is different from the owner/holder of the land on which it stands. See Art 1214 and 1200 of the Civil Co
de.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
