ivative acquisition may result from contracts such as sale and donation/ Arts 2266-2426 and 2427-2470 of the Civil Code respectively or from the will of a deceased person/ testate succession/ or the operation of the law, in cases of in testate succession/
 Arts 826-1125 of the Civil Code/. However, these rules are the subject of separate subjects, the Law of Sales and Law of Succession and are not discussed here. See also the discussion of transfer of ownership right under 3 .3 below.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
