\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428   In a case betwe
en Ato Hailu H/Giorgis and Wro Yeshi H/Mariam in Civil File No 29575 at the Federal First Instance Court, the plaintiff claimed that the defendant is unlawfully holding a house he has built on a 261.25 square meter of land he acquired through transfer and
 
