cquired a right of ownership as per Art 1168(1) of Civil Code and requested the court reject the claim of the plaintiff. She also argued that the plaintiff\rquote 
s action is barred by a 2 years period of limitation from the date when he claims to have been dispossessed.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
