 after examining the evidences produced by both sides and hearing their witnesses}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710659\charrsid11362428 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  identified the following issues;
