\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}Whether the defendant should restore the house to the plaintiff.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710659\charrsid11362428 
