\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 1. What are the requirements for acquisition of ownership through usucaption?
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\tx4215\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428  2. Did the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
