\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 The state shall be liable to third parties who acquired title based up
 on deeds which was not issued in accordance with the law or which was issued by authority having no jurisdiction, or which the authority failed to cancel. See Art 1198.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
