\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 Ditches that lie on the boundary line are presumed to be owned by the owner/holder on whose land the embankment is made. This presumption may also be
 rebutted by proof to the contrary. See Art 1202.
