 bare owner over the thing. Where a usufructuary fails to comply with this provision and the bare owner loses his right of ownership, he shall be liable to compensate the bare owner as if he himself caused the loss or damage of the rights of the bare owne
r. See Art 1342 of the Civil Code. 
