He has the duty to refrain from any kind of interference with the right of the usufructuary to possess, use and enjoy the thing and c
ollect and use its fruits. For example, he cannot change the thing, which is subject of the usufruct nor can he use or exploit the thing or interfere with the possession of the thing.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}He must undertake major repairs as defined under Arts 1337 and 1338, which are not result of the usufructuary\rquote s fault. 

\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}He has an obligation to cover extra ordinary charges. Art 1315 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li600\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin600\itap0\pararsid91394 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91394\charrsid11362428 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11362428 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 
 From the discussions made above regarding the obligations of the usufructuary, we can identify the rights of the bare owner. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91394 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91394\charrsid11362428 
