ch as right of way or right to cross a parcel of land on foot, with animals, during the dead season, across fields, rights of pasture, watering animals, wood-cutting, irrigation.  See Art 1371 of the Civil Code.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
