st-degree relationship with the seller have a priority right over those having a second-degree relation ship. See Art 1391 and 842-851 of the Civil Code. Where the beneficiaries have the same degree of relationship, they shall exercise the right of recove
r
y together and shall become joint owners of the immovable recovered. See Art 1393 of the Civil Code. However, among persons who are in the same degree of relationship, those who live on the land or participate by their personal work in its exploitation ar
