 given priority over others. See Art 1392 of the Civil Code. Furthermore, Art 1396 excludes right of recovery of relatives where the immovable transferred is situated in urban area/ town planning area/ or where it mainly consists of a dwelling house or so
me other building.  These provisions also imply that the right of recovery relatives under is limited to cases where rural farmland communally held by a family/ rest land/ is transferred.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
