{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\fs24\insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 CONDITIONS FOR THE EXERCISE OF RIGHT OF RECOVERY{\*\bkmkend _Toc229915091}
