\b\i\fs28\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 {\*\bkmkstart _Toc229915095}7.2.1 DEFINITION AND REQUIREMENTS FOR VALIDITY{\*\bkmkend _Toc229915095}
