\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 4.\tab}The beneficiary must exercise his rights before the thing is sold by auction in case of attachment. See Art 1421.
