\par A provision prohibiting assignment or attachment shall be of no effect unless it is made in writing and it specifies the duration of the prohibition, which may not exceed 20 years or the life of the transferee. See Arts 1430, and 1431.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398 
