\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2119398\charrsid11362428 1. Define the concept of public domain and distinguish it from the private domain of the state.
\par 2. What are the criteria used to classify things as things forming part of the public domain? Discuss.
\par 3. Enumerate things, which are considered as public domain by nature. 
\par 4. Enumerate things, which are considered as public domain because of their purpose.
\par 5. Define expropriation and indirect expropriation and discuss their differences and similarities.
\par  6. Discuss the concept of public interest under the civil code and proclamation no 455/2005.            
\par 7. Discuss the procedures to be followed during expropriation under the civil Code and proclamation no 455/2005.
